00:12:21.950 --> 00:12:23.034 position:50% align:center
Did that happen?

00:12:23.118 --> 00:12:24.577 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Mh-hm.

00:12:24.661 --> 00:12:29.874 position:50% align:center
My life is K.O. after K.O.--
with no ref to stop the fight.

00:12:29.958 --> 00:12:32.585 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
<i>Uramichi Oniisan.</i>

00:12:32.669 --> 00:12:34.838 position:50% align:center
Well? You ready? C'mon, kids!

