00:13:00.280 --> 00:13:01.489 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Hey, kids!

00:13:01.573 --> 00:13:03.158 position:50% align:center
Our friends Mister Bunny
and Mister Bear

00:13:03.241 --> 00:13:05.493 position:50% align:center
