a game with you!

00:13:05.577 --> 00:13:06.578 position:50% align:center
Is that okay?

00:13:06.661 --> 00:13:08.747 position:50% align:center
[KIDS]
Yeah, that's okay!

00:13:08.830 --> 00:13:10.248 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Wow!

00:13:10.331 --> 00:13:12.459 position:50% align:center
