00:13:14.794 --> 00:13:17.422 position:50% align:center
What kinda game do you
wanna play, buddy?

00:13:17.505 --> 00:13:19.758 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
I...

00:13:19.841 --> 00:13:21.009 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA RECORDING]
I want to play something

00:13:21.092 --> 00:13:23.636 position:50% align:center
