00:13:24.929 --> 00:13:27.140 position:50% align:center
In that case, I've got
just the perfect thing!

00:13:27.223 --> 00:13:30.393 position:50% align:center
Seems to me that you and these
little rascals should play tag!

00:13:30.477 --> 00:13:31.895 position:50% align:center
Bunnies are real fast,

00:13:31.978 --> 00:13:33.813 position:50% align:center
so if you wanna catch him
you'll have to be relentless!

00:13:33.897 --> 00:13:35.148 position:50% align:center
[KIDS]
Yeah!

00:13:35.231 --> 00:13:37.317 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA RECORDING]
I can't wait, hip-hop!

00:13:37.400 --> 00:13:38.568 position:50% align:center
And every time they catch you,

00:13:38.651 --> 00:13:41.404 position:50% align:center
