funny for them, right?

00:13:41.488 --> 00:13:43.281 position:50% align:center
Okay, kids! Go crazy!

00:13:43.365 --> 00:13:45.617 position:50% align:center
[KIDS laughing]

00:13:45.700 --> 00:13:48.161 position:50% align:center
[EDEI]
Great hustle, guys!

00:13:48.244 --> 00:13:51.998 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
Uramichi!

00:13:52.082 --> 00:13:54.584 position:50% align:center
