You're the one who's always
saying you wanna get funny.

00:14:03.093 --> 00:14:04.594 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
I have never said that.

00:14:04.678 --> 00:14:06.388 position:50% align:center
I was just helping
you practice.

00:14:06.471 --> 00:14:07.806 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
Never said it! Not once!

00:14:07.889 --> 00:14:10.350 position:50% align:center
You say it whenever
you get drunk, silly.

00:14:10.433 --> 00:14:13.186 position:50% align:center
You think it'll make
you popular with girls.

00:14:14.729 --> 00:14:15.814 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
He's lying, right?

00:14:15.897 --> 00:14:17.774 position:50% align:center
[KUMATANI]
No, you say that a lot.

00:14:17.857 --> 00:14:19.275 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
No way.

00:14:19.359 --> 00:14:21.403 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI] Why not take off
your costume? Isn't it hot?

00:14:21.486 --> 00:14:23.238 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
Huh? Oh, um--

00:14:23.321 --> 00:14:25.198 position:50% align:center
[KUMATANI] He says he doesn't
like to talk to you face to face

00:14:25.281 --> 00:14:28.993 position:50% align:center
