because your eyes are so scary.

00:14:29.077 --> 00:14:30.328 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
The hell, bro?

00:14:30.412 --> 00:14:32.330 position:50% align:center
How can you stab me in
the back like it's nothin'?

00:14:32.414 --> 00:14:33.915 position:50% align:center
[KUMATANI]
We were never allies.

00:14:33.998 --> 00:14:35.291 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
This is ridiculous!

00:14:35.375 --> 00:14:38.169 position:50% align:center
