for the same reason!

00:14:38.253 --> 00:14:42.173 position:50% align:center
Ah! It's his deadpan face!
That's the worst one!

00:14:46.803 --> 00:14:52.600 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA] Ugh. Uramichi,
just gimme a hint.

00:14:52.684 --> 00:14:55.437 position:50% align:center
What am I supposed to do, huh?!

00:14:55.520 --> 00:14:58.231 position:50% align:center
[GOD]
Tobikichi Usahara, 28 years old.

00:14:58.314 --> 00:14:59.733 position:50% align:center
This man behind the bunny suit

00:14:59.816 --> 00:15:02.944 position:50% align:center
