or junior, in college.

00:15:03.028 --> 00:15:06.990 position:50% align:center
He still uses a piggy bank.
It is frequently empty.

00:15:07.073 --> 00:15:09.534 position:50% align:center
C'mon, tell me.

00:15:11.494 --> 00:15:15.081 position:50% align:center
Hey, uh, waiter? Could we
get a couple hot sakés?

00:15:15.165 --> 00:15:17.917 position:50% align:center
[GOD]
Mitsuo Kumatani, 28 years old.

00:15:18.001 --> 00:15:21.338 position:50% align:center
Graduated from the same college
as Usahara and Uramichi.

00:15:21.421 --> 00:15:23.048 position:50% align:center
He's actually quite observant,

00:15:23.131 --> 00:15:26.134 position:50% align:center
but he isn't the type to put
his perceptiveness to use.

00:15:26.217 --> 00:15:27.802 position:50% align:center
He wears the bear suit.

00:15:27.886 --> 00:15:30.263 position:50% align:center
And a couple saké cups, please.

00:15:30.347 --> 00:15:33.892 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA] If I was funny,
I'd get all the girls.

00:15:33.975 --> 00:15:35.560 position:50% align:center
He needs some water.

00:15:35.643 --> 00:15:38.271 position:50% align:center
Bring us a big glass
of water, too, please!

00:15:38.355 --> 00:15:41.232 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA snoring]

00:15:45.070 --> 00:15:47.072 position:50% align:center
Thanks for joining us today!

00:15:47.155 --> 00:15:50.492 position:50% align:center
We'll see you kids next time!
So take care until then!

00:15:50.575 --> 00:15:52.202 position:50% align:center
[UTANO]
We hope you had fun!

00:15:52.285 --> 00:15:54.412 position:50% align:center
If you enjoyed the show,
then keep tuning in!

00:15:54.496 --> 00:15:55.413 position:50% align:center
[IKETERU]
Bye-bye!

00:15:55.497 --> 00:15:56.039 position:50% align:center
[UTANO]
Bye-bye!

00:15:56.122 --> 00:15:57.832 position:50% align:center
[GIRL F]
Bye-bye!

00:15:57.916 --> 00:15:59.834 position:50% align:center
Okay. Cut!

00:15:59.918 --> 00:16:02.754 position:50% align:center
Great stuff, guys.
Another good hustle!

00:16:04.297 --> 00:16:06.341 position:50% align:center
[BOTH grunt]

00:16:06.424 --> 00:16:11.012 position:50% align:center
[GOD] Iketeru Daga, 27 years
old. A singer Oniisan.

00:16:11.096 --> 00:16:12.597 position:50% align:center
