He has the looks of a blue-blood
and the mind of a pig.

00:16:21.106 --> 00:16:23.024 position:50% align:center
He loves crass, dirty jokes

00:16:23.108 --> 00:16:27.028 position:50% align:center
and he's incapable of reading
a room or catching a hint.

00:16:28.113 --> 00:16:29.823 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:16:29.906 --> 00:16:31.449 position:50% align:center
So, what time is it?

00:16:31.533 --> 00:16:33.827 position:50% align:center
Is that just a bracelet to you?

00:16:33.910 --> 00:16:37.706 position:50% align:center
[GOD] He also has a difficult
time with analog clocks.

00:16:39.416 --> 00:16:43.086 position:50% align:center
[GOD] Utano Tadano, 32 years
old. A singer Oneesan.

00:16:43.169 --> 00:16:45.505 position:50% align:center
She graduated from a
prestigious music school

00:16:45.588 --> 00:16:48.717 position:50% align:center
and then proceeded to fail,
first as a pop idol,

00:16:48.800 --> 00:16:51.428 position:50% align:center
then as a singer of
traditional <i>enka</i> ballads,

00:16:51.511 --> 00:16:54.097 position:50% align:center
and finally as a
nightclub jazz singer.

00:16:54.180 --> 00:16:55.932 position:50% align:center
Now she's here.

00:17:01.521 --> 00:17:03.189 position:50% align:center
[GOD] Incidentally,
she has now been living

00:17:03.273 --> 00:17:07.152 position:50% align:center
