00:20:05.288 --> 00:20:06.289 position:50% align:center
Dick Seaman.

00:20:06.373 --> 00:20:07.791 position:50% align:center
[IKETERU laughs]

00:20:07.874 --> 00:20:11.920 position:50% align:center
[IKETERU]
Seaman. Oh, no. No, no.

00:20:12.003 --> 00:20:14.089 position:50% align:center
[IKETERU]
<i>Uramichi Oniisan.</i>

00:20:14.172 --> 00:20:17.634 position:50% align:center
[EDEI] Okay. Let's get
back to it, people!

00:20:17.717 --> 00:20:22.097 position:50% align:center
Oh, hey there, kids!
<i>Konnichiwa</i> !

00:20:22.180 --> 00:20:25.058 position:50% align:center
