some art with us?

00:20:25.141 --> 00:20:27.477 position:50% align:center
Iketeru Oniisan is
gonna join us soon.

00:20:27.560 --> 00:20:29.979 position:50% align:center
He just needs some time
to get it together.

00:20:30.063 --> 00:20:32.816 position:50% align:center
[BOY B] Is Iketeru Oniisan
not together right now?

00:20:32.899 --> 00:20:34.275 position:50% align:center
Nope, not even a little!

00:20:34.359 --> 00:20:37.028 position:50% align:center
In fact, he's on the
verge of collapse.

00:20:38.238 --> 00:20:39.614 position:50% align:center
Learning moment, kids.

00:20:39.698 --> 00:20:41.616 position:50% align:center
If you don't make time for
breaks when you're at work,

