That's when exhaustion
gobbles up your brain cells.

00:20:46.371 --> 00:20:48.289 position:50% align:center
Should we warn Iketeru?

00:20:48.373 --> 00:20:50.000 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
It's too late for him.

00:20:50.083 --> 00:20:51.793 position:50% align:center
[GIRL G]
That's so sad.

00:20:51.876 --> 00:20:54.087 position:50% align:center
Let's move along. Utano Oneesan!

