I was thinking we could
draw our friends today!

00:21:01.052 --> 00:21:02.762 position:50% align:center
You wouldn't mind
going first, would you?

00:21:02.846 --> 00:21:05.974 position:50% align:center
Just draw one of your pals and
introduce them to the class!

00:21:06.057 --> 00:21:07.183 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
You wanna meet my friend?

00:21:07.267 --> 00:21:09.102 position:50% align:center
[KIDS]
Yeah!

00:21:15.650 --> 00:21:16.693 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Done!

00:21:16.776 --> 00:21:17.861 position:50% align:center
[UTANO]
What is this?

00:21:17.944 --> 00:21:21.239 position:50% align:center
Hold on. I can't--
But why? Just why?

00:21:21.322 --> 00:21:22.490 position:50% align:center
[URAMICHI]
Let me explain!

00:21:22.574 --> 00:21:24.492 position:50% align:center
Technically, it's hard
to say if we're friends,

00:21:24.576 --> 00:21:26.745 position:50% align:center
but I do know this little
bird man pretty well.

00:21:26.828 --> 00:21:28.663 position:50% align:center
He haunts my dreams!

00:21:28.747 --> 00:21:30.415 position:50% align:center
So <i>kawaii</i> !

00:21:30.498 --> 00:21:32.334 position:50% align:center
[UTANO]
Are you okay?

00:21:32.417 --> 00:21:33.960 position:50% align:center
If I slip up and
admit that I'm not,

00:21:34.044 --> 00:21:36.254 position:50% align:center
it'll jump to take
advantage of my weakness.

00:21:36.338 --> 00:21:39.966 position:50% align:center
There's no trace of
pity in those eyes.

00:21:40.050 --> 00:21:42.594 position:50% align:center
Maybe you should go
take a break, too.

00:21:43.803 --> 00:21:46.514 position:50% align:center
[UTANO]
<i>Uramichi Oniisan</i> ?

00:21:46.598 --> 00:21:47.849 position:50% align:center
Okay, cut!

00:21:47.932 --> 00:21:50.393 position:50% align:center
We're gonna call it a wrap
for the day, all right?

00:21:50.477 --> 00:21:52.395 position:50% align:center
Great hustle, team!

00:21:55.732 --> 00:21:56.691 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA]
I mean, like, seriously.

00:21:56.775 --> 00:21:58.985 position:50% align:center
What's Uramichi's deal?

00:21:59.069 --> 00:22:00.278 position:50% align:center
He doesn't have a single hobby

00:22:00.362 --> 00:22:02.739 position:50% align:center
aside from weight
training, right?

00:22:02.822 --> 00:22:07.494 position:50% align:center
One of these days, I'mma sit
him down for a talk. Heh.

00:22:07.577 --> 00:22:08.578 position:50% align:center
I'll let him know
that the reason

00:22:08.661 --> 00:22:10.413 position:50% align:center
those muscles don't get him laid

00:22:10.497 --> 00:22:14.793 position:50% align:center
is cause he acts like
a mopey killjoy...?

00:22:17.462 --> 00:22:21.966 position:50% align:center
[GOD] In that moment,
indifference was buried in rage!

00:22:22.050 --> 00:22:25.053 position:50% align:center
[USAHARA screams]